===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[三]] || [[ヶ]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
[[三]] (さん, ''san'') "three" + [[ヶ]] ([[箇]], か, ''ka''), the counter for months + [[月]] (げつ, ''getsu'') "month"

===Noun===
'''三ヶ月''' ([[さんかげつ]], ''sankagetsu'')

# [[三箇月]]: three months (duration)

